            <title>[SOLR-528] Given but undefined default search field in schema.xml causes cryptic error message</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-528</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When a default search field is given in schema.xml but the field itself is not defined, a generic SolrException with the message &quot;Schema parsing failed&quot; is thrown. Only further down in the stacktrace the message &quot;unknown field &apos;foobar&apos;&quot; appears (and does not indicate where the unknown field is referenced).&lt;/p&gt;</description>
